data.description: This home is one of very few homes in our area priced below $300,000. It has features not even found in higher priced homes which makes it even better. The sellers are ready to sell.  They will pay off the Solar Panels ($40,000 value) with a full price offer.  They are offering $3,000  toward the Buyer's closing costs.   The extra features include the following:  Smart Home Technology, lights can be controlled by the Smart Home Panel, Nest Learning Thermostat, Door Keypad, Security System, Doorbell camera and Blink smart exterior cameras on front and rear of house. The bedrooms are wired for ceiling fans. There is new capacitator in the A/C  unit.  The HVAC ductwork has been cleaned and sprayed with sealant to insulate making it more efficient.  Located on a cul-de-sac across from a nature preserve makes for very little traffic.  The Whisper Creek Subdivision location is convenient to Pace and Milton.
